sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor JobSeeker as "Job Seeker"
    participant Client as "Nuxt Client (Frontend)"
    participant Server as "Nitro Server (Backend)"
    participant DB as "Cloudflare D1"
    participant Ollama as "Ollama API (:11434)"

    %% Scenario 1: AI Onboarding Chat & Profile Extraction
    Note over JobSeeker, Ollama: Scenario 1: AI Onboarding Chat & Profile Extraction
    JobSeeker->>Client: Type and send onboarding message
    Client->>Server: POST /api/chat { message }
    activate Server
    Server->>DB: Validate Session & Retrieve User ID
    Server->>DB: INSERT INTO chat_messages (user_id, role, content)
    Server->>DB: SELECT role, content FROM chat_messages (full history)
    DB-->>Server: Return chronological history
    Server->>Ollama: POST /api/chat (gemma3:270m, history + interview prompt)
    activate Ollama
    Ollama-->>Server: Return chat response (Aria's reply)
    deactivate Ollama
    Server->>DB: INSERT INTO chat_messages (assistant response)
    
    %% Non-blocking background data extraction
    Note over Server, Ollama: Async Profile Data Extraction
    Server->>Ollama: POST /api/chat (history + extraction prompt)
    activate Ollama
    Ollama-->>Server: Return extracted JSON profile data
    deactivate Ollama
    Server->>DB: UPDATE jobseeker_profiles (set fields & completeness score)
    
    Server-->>Client: Return { reply, profile, completeness }
    deactivate Server
    Client-->>JobSeeker: Display Aria's response & update progress bar

    %% Scenario 2: Post-Application AI Screening
    Note over JobSeeker, Ollama: Scenario 2: Post-Application AI Screening
    JobSeeker->>Client: Send message during screening interview
    Client->>Server: POST /api/jobs/screening { jobId, message }
    activate Server
    Server->>DB: Fetch job details, candidate profile, and app status
    DB-->>Server: Return application & profile data
    Server->>DB: UPDATE job_applications (append user message to chat history)
    Server->>Ollama: POST /api/chat (granite4:350m, screening prompt + chat history)
    activate Ollama
    Ollama-->>Server: Return screening question (or Concluded message with [CONCLUDED])
    deactivate Ollama
    Server->>DB: UPDATE job_applications (append AI message to chat history)
    
    alt If Response contains '[CONCLUDED]'
        Note over Server, Ollama: Candidate Evaluation
        Server->>Ollama: POST /api/chat (transcript + eval prompt)
        activate Ollama
        Ollama-->>Server: Return SCORE: XX, SUMMARY: ...
        deactivate Ollama
        Server->>DB: UPDATE job_applications SET ai_screening_completed=1, ai_screening_score=XX, ai_screening_summary=...
    end
    
    Server-->>Client: Return { reply, completed, score/summary }
    deactivate Server
    Client-->>JobSeeker: Show final message & update UI status
